<HEADLINE>
<P>
EARTH FIRST! 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
In "The Monkeywrenchers," I came across the sentence: "Thanks in part to the 
Reagan Administration's anti-environmentalist policies . . . " It was laying 
there like undisputed fact. 
</P>
<P>
This was supposed to be a truthful, accurate story. What is here is opinion. 
Opinion needs to be on the Opinion Page, or at least so noted. It is a shame 
that what could otherwise be a great newspaper stoops to blending its politics 
with the news. 
</P>
<P>
BOB W. JAMES 
</P>
<P>
La Mirada 
</P>
