READ THE LABEL 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
Have Governor Deukmejian and the poison-spraying crews in California read the 
warnings on the malathion bottles? 
</P>
<P>
They warn against spraying children, animals, fish, and bees. 
</P>
<P>
They warn against inhaling the poison, getting the spray on hands or in eyes. 
</P>
<P>
Which is more important -- subsidizing the pesticide manufacturers and 
agribusinesses, or protecting American families, their animals, their food? 
</P>
<P>
MARY P. AUSTIN 
</P>
<P>
Pauma Valley 
