<HEADLINE>
<P>
ROAD NOTES 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
Caltrans plans the following closures on San Gabriel Valley freeways this week: 
</P>
<P>
Two lanes on the westbound Pomona Freeway (60) in the City of Industry from 
southbound 605 Freeway to Santa Anita Avenue will be closed today from 6 a.m. 
to noon. 
</P>
<P>
One lane on the eastbound San Bernardino Freeway (10) in the city of El Monte 
from Peck Road to the San Gabriel River will be closed Tuesday from 8 a.m. to 2 
p.m. 
</P>
<P>
Two lanes on the southbound Orange Freeway (57) in the city of Pomona from 
Madera Road to Kuehner Drive will be closed Wednesday from 8 a.m. to 3 p.m. 
</P>
