<HEADLINE>
<P>
NON-TRADITIONAL JOB? 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
Do you or someone you know make all or part of your living through a 
non-traditional job or occupation (maybe it's even a bit shady)? I'd like to 
hear from you. 
</P>
<P>
I'm studying how Americans make a living and I'll treat your reply with total 
confidentiality. Just send an address to "Jobs," P.O. Box 171, Eureka, CA 
95502. I'll send you a short questionnaire so that you can become a part of a 
national study of the American entrepreneurial spirit. 
</P>
<P>
PETE PETERSON 
</P>
<P>
EUREKA 
</P>
