facility. ; Photo, John I. Miller, chief of flight operations, in cockpit of an 
MD-11. ; Photo, Joe Ornelas, MD-11 flight test manager in Yuma, Ariz. ; Photo, 
The MD-11 is the subject of one of the fastest-paced certification programs in 
industry history. TOM KELSEY / Los Angeles Times 
</P>
</GRAPHIC>
