-- ECONOMY; THINK TANKS; CANON INC; TOSHIBA CORP; FUJITSU LTD; HITACHI LTD; 
MATSUHITA ELECTRIC INDUSTRIAL CO LTD; EMPLOYMENT -- WOMEN 
</P>
</SUBJECT>
</DOC>
