of CBS' "Designing Women" at their Los Angeles Biltmore wedding a year ago. 
Associated Press; Photo, COLOR, And right, McRaney with his "Major Dad" family, 
from left, Nicole Dubuc, Shanna Reed, Chelsea Hertford and Marisa Ryan. 
</P>
