was seriously wounded in a shoot-out outside her home in Santa Clarita after 
the assailants followed her home in an apparent attempt to steal her car. One 
suspect was killed, above, and three others were arrested. GARY THORNHILL / For 
The Times 
</P>
</GRAPHIC>
